"{\"uid\": \"athens-times.com-the-mens-national-pole-against-australia-for-positions-5-8-at-the-olympics\", \"text\": \"Athens Times  -  The men's national pole was defeated in an incredible way by Serbia in the final seconds of the quarterfinal and stayed out of medal zone. The obligations of blue-white are not completed in Paris, as it will compete in ranking games for positions 5-8. There he will meet Australia, which was defeated by the U.S. in the penalty. As for semi-final couples, these are Serbia - USA and Croatia - Hungary.  Athens Times  News about Greece and the World.\"}"